OL,3,CInitiative to help revive local high
OL,4,Cstreet
OL,6,FAn initiative to revive Galashiels'
OL,7,Fhigh street is coming to the town as
OL,8,Fpart of a national scheme to tackle
OL,9,Fempty shops.
OL,11,FThe Vacant Shops Academy is a UK-wide
OL,12,Fprogramme which aims to understand the
OL,13,Fbarriers which keep shops closed, and
OL,14,Fwork with councils and Business
OL,15,FImprovement Districts (BIDs) to re-
OL,16,Fopen their doors.
OL,18,FDuring the 2024 Galashiels BID
OL,19,Fconsultation, empty units were cited
OL,20,Fas the number one concern for the town.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
