PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776258665
OL,3,CInitiative to help revive local high
OL,4,Cstreet
OL,6,FThe Vacant Shops Academy has already
OL,7,Fworked in places across the UK,
OL,8,Fhelping towns and smaller high streets
OL,9,Funderstand their vacant units and take
OL,10,Faction to bring them back into use.
OL,12,FThe approach taken by the academy is
OL,13,Fto audit existing vacant units, and
OL,14,Fassess gaps in the town to determine
OL,15,Fwhat types of businesses could make
OL,16,Fgood additions to the high street.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
