CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776258665
OL,3,CInitiative to help revive local high
OL,4,Cstreet
OL,6,FThe academy then aims to help engage
OL,7,Fwith lettings agents and landlords,
OL,8,Fand then facilitate the lettings
OL,9,Fprocess and encourage potential
OL,10,Ftenants.
OL,12,FFinally, advice is offered to help
OL,13,Fbusinesses use social media and
OL,14,Ftraditional outlets to promote their
OL,15,Foffer and share positive updates with
OL,16,Fthe wider community.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
