CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1776258665
OL,3,CInitiative to help revive local high
OL,4,Cstreet
OL,6,FA Vacant Shops Academy spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's not just about listing
OL,8,Fempty properties - it's about
OL,9,Funderstanding the real barriers,
OL,10,Fworking closely with landlords and
OL,11,Fagents, and creating realistic
OL,12,Fopportunities for businesses to take
OL,13,Fon space.
OL,15,F"It's a proven, partnership-led
OL,16,Fapproach that's already supporting
OL,17,Ftowns across the UK and we're pleased
OL,18,Fto be bringing that experience to
OL,19,FGalashiels."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
